<td valign="MIDDLE"><font face="Verdana" size="2" color="000000">Alright,friend.My items,as of now,at lev 20,are...<br>
Flowing Black Robe,AC 8,+3 Int,+5 Stamina<br>
2x Jaded Silver Wristbands,+10 mana/HP,2 AC each<br>
Raw Silk Sleeves,2 AC<br>
2x Gold Earstuds,+3 Int each<br>
Raw Silk Veil,2 AC<br>
Halo of Light,3 AC,Greater Lightsource<br>
Raw Silk Gloves,AC 2<br>
Raw Silk Pants,AC 4<br>
Bear Hide Belt,AC 4<br>
Bear Hide Boots,AC 5<br>
Polar Bear Cloak,AC 5,+15 SV vs Cold<br>
Skull of Jhen'Tra +20 Mana,+3 SV vs Magic<br>
Stein of Moggok,+10 Int,+5 Dex,+25 SV vs Disease,3 charges of Light Healing(heals 30 HP per charge)<br>
Silver Rose Engagement Ring +2 Int<br>
Band of Rodcet Nife,+3 Int,+10 mana<br>
My AC,with 'Shielding',is 231,and I have 30 Poison Resist,50 Disease Resist,40 Magic Resist,40 cold resist,and 20 Fire resist.I have 415 HPs.136 int.I had all these items at lev 15-20...and 15 was simple for me.Goto Qeynos Hills,kill rabid bears,and turn in pelts to Priestess Caulria for about half a bub of ep.Easy kills,too.Just watchout for Holly and Cros.They kill you if they see you fighting an animal(bear or wolf)At 16,I kited Scythe Beetles,lev 18-20 mid-high Red NPCs.About half a bub of ep off each of em.Made 4 bubs in a day.Just awful loot(Fire Beetle Eyez.Ohhhh,whooopie.)</font></td></tr></table></td></tr><tr bgcolor="DDDDDD">
